data.description: Welcome to your perfect Jersey Shore home! This gorgeous beauty features 4 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a conveniently placed powder room on the first level! This home has been put to date in the most immaculate way possible with a new HVAC system, new roof, updated siding, new garage doors, and a full upgrade of interiors. Walk into an elegant foyer with a high ceiling boasting space above all! This home comes with a large living room in the front with an open concept layout featuring a 6-8-person dining room. A renovated kitchen sits at the heart of this home overlooking a large entertainment room with easy backyard access through your sliding doors and tons of natural light. The garage in this home is perfect, featuring more than enough space for all storage! Upstairs, we find 2 full bathrooms and 4 large bedrooms including a primary suite with a walk-in closet! You cannot miss the opportunity to live seconds away from the entertainment of Manahawkin and the Barnegat area while minutes from the shore. This home sits a minute away from the Garden State Parkway and is ready to be yours!
